    <content><![CDATA[<p>杭电英语面试常见问题：</p>
<pre><code>你为什么选择杭电/为什么来杭州
你的研究生计划是？
介绍一下你的家乡
介绍一下你的大学
你最喜欢的一门课是什么？为什么？
感兴趣的研究方向
以后想成为什么，为此你需要怎么做？（研究生计划）</code></pre><p>英语自我介绍：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">	Good morning,every teacher.It&#39;s really agreat honor to have this</span><br><span class="line">opportunity for an interview.And I hope I can make a good performance today. </span><br><span class="line">	First,let me introduce myself briefly.My name is ZZQ,and I am 23 years old. I come from HengYang city, </span><br><span class="line">HuNan Province.And I majored in the Internet of things at WuHan University of technology.I was studying </span><br><span class="line">at home since I graduated in June 2019. During that time,I finish most of the C Plus programming at PAT.</span><br><span class="line">And I do the algorithm problem at leetcode now.I really enjoyed programming,and I hope I can concentrate </span><br><span class="line">on study and research in this field in my graduate time.</span><br><span class="line">	OK, that&#39;s all.Thank you very much for your listening and attention.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>各位老师早上好，很荣幸能参加贵校的面试。我叫ZZQ，23岁，毕业于武汉理工大学计算机科学与技术学院。</p>
]]></content>
